olygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Lego NES is discounted to its lowest price ever for Insiders members", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T13:25:47+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/chorus/uploads/chorus_asset/file/22421966/INVI_S1_FG_101_00365322_Still034.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Prime Video heard you, <em>Invincible </em>fans \u2014 the upcoming third season will not have a mid-season break, unlike last time.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The announcement came in a cheeky teaser released Thursday by Prime Video, where Mark (Steven Yeun) and Cecil (Walton Goggins) discuss the dramatic events that closed out season 2 (namely, Mark getting his ass kicked by a new Viltrumite in town) and Mark\u2019s preparation (or is it Yeun\u2019s?) for their next chapter defending Earth.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Amazon also released a promotional image with Mark\u2019s new blue suit:</p>\n<img src=\"https://platf", "id": 1329839, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/tv/465898/invincible-season-3-date-teaser-no-midseason-break", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Invincible season 3 teaser promises no mid-season break this time", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T13:00:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/D20-SEATTLE.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,55.3890625,75.153273809524\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Dimension 20\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/tabletop-games/24130879/dimension-20-ticketmaster-madison-square-garden-ticket-pricing-controversy-gauntlet-in-the-garden\">Madison Square Garden show</a> in January 2025 is already sold out, but if you\u2019re on the West Coast, you\u2019re in luck \u2014 Dropout announced that three <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/actual-play/446227/never-stop-blowing-up-dimension-20-cast-interview\">Dimension 20</a> shows are coming to West Coast cities next year.\u00a0</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">At the Hollywood Bowl in Los Angeles on June 1, 2025, the Bad Kids of Dimension 20\u2019s <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/tabletop-games/24", "id": 1329277, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/news/465862/dimension-20-west-coast-tour-2025", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Dimension 20 is going on a West Coast tour", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T10:24:16+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/SF6-soundtrack-cover.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">I\u2019m a big fan of ambient lo-fi music, but sometimes I need something to <em>wake me up</em> \u2014 which is especially true following a three-day weekend, as many readers are probably feeling right now. And what better way to get hyped for the day/week/month ahead than with the bombastic and eclectic grooves of the <em>Street Fighter 6 </em>soundtrack? Right now you can get the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CRMDJZDN\">collector\u2019s edition vinyl set</a> from Amazon for around $66 (was $170), a 61% discount. That\u2019s a lot of 6s for one deal, and we wish we had something more clever to say about that, but again, it\u2019s the first day after a three-day weekend and we o", "id": 1328292, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/good-deals/465793/street-fighter-6-ost-vinyl-sf6", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Street Fighter 6 collector\u2019s edition vinyl soundtrack is $66 at Amazon", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T09:00:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"A large man with a miniature giant space hamster on his shoulder is lead through a crowded ballroom by a spirit dressed in red maple leaves.\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Katerina Ladon/Wizards of the Coast\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/Ballroom_Katerina-Ladon-copy.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The revised <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/dnd-dungeons-dragons\">Dungeons &amp; Dragons</a> <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/23827632/dnd-dungeons-dragons-keepsake-games-dungeon-masters-guide-dmg\"><em>Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide</em> (2024)</a> will begin trickling out to fans around the world soon thanks to <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/dnd-dungeons-dragons/444017/dnd-beyond-homebrew-changes-canceled-fan-outcry\">Wizards of the Coast</a>\u2019s aggressively tiered <a href=\"https:", "id": 1327739, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/dnd-dungeons-dragons/465448/matt-mercer-deborah-ann-woll-consultants-dmg-dungeon-masters-guide", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Matt Mercer, Deborah Ann Woll, other professional DMs helped write the new Dungeon Master\u2019s Guide", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T08:25:48+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"Michael Keaton\u2019s Batman with cowl on from the 1989 movie, his eyes lit but mouth in the shadows\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Warner Bros. Pictures\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/batman_4k_86.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-drop-cap has-text-align-none\">Usually, a sequel to one of the biggest movies of all time would be carefully concocted in a Hollywood boardroom to maximize four-quadrant potential. John Jackson Miller wrote his continuation of <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/23389073/tim-burton-batman-silent-motion-picture-edit\">Tim Burton\u2019s mega-hit <em>Batman</em></a> over the last year in his memorabilia-filled office in central Wisconsin.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Miller has been thinking about how to follow up Burton\u2019s <em>Batman</em> since he reviewed the film for t", "id": 1327396, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/books/465391/batman-resurrection-book-tim-burton-sequel", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Tim Burton\u2019s Batman has a new sequel, driven by one fan\u2019s burning questions", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-15T05:41:58+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"Image: Niantic / The Pok\u00e9mon Company via Polygon\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/pokemon-go-magnetic-study.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><strong>\u201cMagnetic Study\u201d</strong> is an electric-type focused event taking place in the \u201cMax Out\u201d season of <em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/pokemon-go/38713\">Pok\u00e9mon Go</a></em>.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Running Oct. 15-17, each day of the event has a unique bonus to take advantage of, as well as Timed Research focused around one of three Pok\u00e9mon \u2014 Magnemite, Plusle, and Minun.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">These Pok\u00e9mon can also be caught throughout the event via Field Research, and all have an increased shiny chance if they are missing from your collection.</p>\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channe", "id": 1326573, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/pokemon-go-guide/465770/magnetic-study-plusle-minun-magnemite-timed-research-event", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "\u2018Magnetic Study\u2019 Plusle Timed Research and event guide in Pok\u00e9mon Go", "vote": 0}]